4.3 scikit-learn を用いた線形回帰の実行例: 単回帰分析¶

In [35]:
# sklearn.linear_model.LinearRegression 
from sklearn import linear_model
clf = linear_model.LinearRegression() # 

X = df_cleansed.loc[:, ['wind_max']] #  "wind_max ()" 
Y = df_cleansed.loc[:, ['wind_peak']] #  "wind_peak" 
clf.fit(X, Y) # 

coef = float(clf.coef_); print(coef) # 
intercept = float(clf.intercept_); print(intercept) #  () 
##print(clf.score(X, Y)) # 

# 
def wind_peak_regression(wm):
    return float(coef * wm + intercept)
